### 学校管理模块API测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 0. 准备测试数据

### 0.1 注册管理员用户
# @name schoolAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "school_admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "学校管理员",
  "email": "schooladmin@campus.com",
  "phone": "13900000041",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "teacher"
}

### 0.2 注册普通用户
# @name normalUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "school_user_001",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "普通用户",
  "email": "schooluser@campus.com",
  "phone": "13900000042",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "student"
}

